name: Meshswap protocol
description: meshswap is a unique AMM DEX (Swap, Lend, Farm & Leverage, and Stake) protocol on polygon. No private sale, No presale, Community-driven $MESH : MESH is not just the incentive booster of the meshswap ecosystem but also the governance token which has a core authority to determine MESH reward distribution. Only MESH stakers can participate in pool voting that determines which pool to distribute more MESHs. MESH stakers can receive an additional 50% of the trading fees from the pool and additional rewards generated from our ecosystem.
